        Should You Negotiate Your Real Estate Agent's Commission?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        What Brisbane sellers need to know about commission rates, when it makes sense to push back, and what you might be giving up when you do.
      </p>
